~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~


How to commence fun times
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

On Windows or Mac OS X, locate the "run_game.py" file and double-click it.

Othewise open a terminal / console and "cd" to the game directory and run:

	python run_game.py


How to master the game
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

You are the blob. Enter each level on the left, exit on the right.
Move with the arrow keys. Press up to jump. Sludge makes you mutate.


